item.title: Which of the following units are SI units?

material.mattext: Which of the following are within the SI system of units?

item.title: Convert [x] gallons per hour to cubic centimeters per second.

material.mattext:
Convert `x` gallons per hour to cubic centimeters per second.

1 gallon = 231 in3

1 in = 2.54 cm

1 hr = 3600 s

Given the following:

1000 ns = 1 μs

1000 μs = 1 ms

1000 ms = 1 s

60 s = 1 min
